title: This Dude Just Took Hot Dogs To The Damn Next Level
text: @avitsii / Via instagram.com ID: 10584322 6. Made by ~amateur~ Swedish chef Fabian Göransson made the meal after watching one too many cooking shows on Netflix. “The big thing right now seems to be “deconstructing” food,” he told BuzzFeed. Facebook: search ID: 10584240 7. He was inspired by “a traditional Swedish dish called Veal Oscar, with the sausage acting as asparagus and the bun as the meat,” Göransson told BuzzFeed.
